Sentencas: Fuel cell systems must not only be thermodynamically efficient, but cost competitive as well.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Since power plant capital costs are typically measured per unit of rated power (i.e., $/kW), one means of attempting an economically attractive product is to design for power.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A proven model of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell (TSOFC) is presented and verified.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The model was used to reveal subtle aspects of enhancing power generation.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Internal reformation, while beneficial to system size and integration, hinders power generation.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Increasing the electrode thicknesses of the TSOFC design can be beneficial to power generation.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Finally, decreasing fuel utilization, at a prescribed operating voltage, is also favorable for power generation.
Titulo: 'Design for power' of a commercial grade tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: These latter trends are explained in view of the common assertions that thinner electrodes and increased fuel utilizations are the means of fuel cell operation enhancement.
